    public class BooleanDropDown
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.form.DropDownChoice<Boolean>
    Shows a drop-down selection for Boolean values. If the model contains a starting null, the null value is shown. If the model contains a true or false value, the null value is hidden. Can be configured to be a required field, or to accept resetting the value back to null.
    Author:
    joao.neves@premium-minds.com
